
Name:

    default : Thread-0

    t1.setName("Pavan");
    t1.getName();

Priority:

    t1.setPriority();//default 5
    t1.setPriority(Thread.MAX_PRIORITY); 10
    t1.setPriority(Thread.MIN_PRIORITY); 1
    t1.setPriority(Thread.NORM_PRIORITY); 5

Read :

    currentThread().getName();
    currentThread().getPriority();


